    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "はい、こちらスマホケースですよ～\nうちらのサイン入りです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Howdy‚ here ya go with the smartphone case‚ y'all.\nIt's signed by us‚ darlin'.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n握手ですか？　もちろんいいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank ya kindly.\nA handshake‚ ya say? Well‚ shucks‚ I'm game.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "あなた、いつもライブに来てくれはる人やん\n今日お話出来て、うちめっちゃ感激やわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y'all always comin' to our concerts‚ ain't ya?\nToday‚ gettin' a chance to chat with ya got me plum tickled.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（……鈴村さん、調子良さそうだな。体調不良には）\n（見えない。俺の気のせいだったか……良かった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Seems like Suzumura-san's in high spirits‚ maybe my worries about her health…）\n（were all for naught. I'm relieved.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "この缶バッチはなぁ、瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんのと\n並べて使うともっと映えるんよ。セットがお得です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ya see‚ darlin'‚ if ya put this button side by side with Rui-chan's and Sumire-chan's‚\nit'll make 'em shine brighter than a sunset. It's a real steal as a set.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_01-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "商売上手？　ほんまに映えるから勧めてるだけやけど\n……ふふ、褒め言葉と思っておきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A savvy saleswoman‚ ya reckon? Well‚ I'm just suggestin' 'cause it's downright fabulous.\n…Hehe‚ I'll take that as a sweet talkin' compliment‚ sugarcube.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
