      "text": "はい、お買い上げありがとうございます～\n気をつけて帰って下さいね。おおきに～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Much obliged for buyin' it‚ hon.\nYa take care now‚ ya hear? Much obliged to ya.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
